data.description: You won’t want to miss this beautiful one-owner, 2-story home in Stone Creek! All of the big-ticket items have been updated with new furnace & AC, new windows & front door, and new exterior paint. The traditional floor plan features a huge kitchen with a great dining area, large center island and tons of cabinet space! It opens to a large family room and walks out onto a freshly stained deck. The main floor also has a formal dining room, sitting room/office space and laundry/drop zone. Upstairs you’ll find a beautiful primary suite with “sitting area” which would be great for a home office or private reading nook. It has double sinks & huge walk-in closet. The other bedrooms are nice-sized and have walk-in closets. A finished lower level has a fantastic rec room, wet bar, ¾ bath and plenty of storage. The west facing home sits on a ¼ acre lot with a fenced backyard, professional landscaping and a huge 4 car garage! Conveniently located close to the clubhouse, schools and Flanagan Lake.
